Ingredience</h2><span class="sc-71yq56-5 bKDBKx">Složení</span><div data-testid="recipe-details-ingredients-counter" class="sc-71yq56-1 fMylAP"><div class="sc-10xen8i-0 jFBvVm"><button data-testid="counter-minus" aria-label="snížit počet porcí" type="button" class="sc-10xen8i-2 sc-10xen8i-3 dMUzui byHMHp"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="100%" height="100%" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 12a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h12a1 1 0 1 1 0 2H6a1 1 0 0 1-1-1" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></button><span data-testid="counter-result" class="sc-10xen8i-1 licmEt"> 8 porcí</span><button data-testid="counter-plus" aria-label="zvýšit počet porcí" type="button" class="sc-10xen8i-2 sc-10xen8i-3 dMUzui byHMHp"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="100%" height="100%" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 5a1 1 0 1 0-2 0v6H5a1 1 0 1 0 0 2h6v6a1 1 0 1 0 2 0v-6h6a1 1 0 1 0 0-2h-6z"></path></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="sc-71yq56-13 hhwrSh"><div class="sc-71yq56-7 bPCpmp"><ul data-testid="recipe-details-ingredients-list" class="sc-71yq56-3 sc-71yq56-4 bxUczQ cEbkvB"><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Tortilla pšeničná <b>2 ks</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Philadephia <b>125 g</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Salátová okurka <b>1 ks</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Krůtí šunka <b>3 plát.</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Sýr tvrdý <b>3 plát.</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Hroznové víno bílé <b> </b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Jablečná kapsička <b> </b></li></ul></div><div class="sc-71yq56-6 hHcvrj"><ul data-testid="recipe-details-ingredients-list" class="sc-71yq56-3 sc-71yq56-4 bxUczQ cEbkvB"><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Tortilla pšeničná <b>2 ks</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Philadephia <b>125 g</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Salátová okurka <b>1 ks</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Krůtí šunka <b>3 plát.</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Sýr tvrdý <b>3 plát.</b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Hroznové víno bílé <b> </b></li><li class="sc-g0if9p-0 dSlvjg">Jablečná kapsička <b> </b></li></ul></div></div></div><div data-testid="recipe-details-cooking-steps" class="sc-1tl93fv-7 leuXbG"><h2 class="sc-1vohui3-0 frUwOm" color="var(--color-neutral700)" data-testid="styled-title" data-stellar="st-web-title" id="">Příprava</h2><ol class="sc-1tl93fv-11 bTERKK"><li data-testid="recipe-details-cooking-step-print" class="sc-1tl93fv-0 brKJtq"><div class="sc-1tl93fv-1 diagqg">1</div><div class="sc-1tl93fv-2 bNfpGN">Z tortil odkrojte okraje tak, abyste místo kruhu získali obdélník. Pomažte je sýrem. První obdélník vyskládejte tenkými kolečky okurky. Zarolujte a dvakrát přepulte.</div></li><li data-testid="recipe-details-cooking-step-print" class="sc-1tl93fv-0 brKJtq"><div class="sc-1tl93fv-1 diagqg">2</div><div class="sc-1tl93fv-2 bNfpGN">Druhou tortilu vyskládejte šunkou, sýrem a postupujte stejně jako u první rolky.</div></li><li data-testid="recipe-details-cooking-step-print" class="sc-1tl93fv-0 brKJtq"><div class="sc-1tl93fv-1 diagqg">3</div><div class="sc-1tl93fv-2 bNfpGN">Svačinu doplňte o minibalení bezpeckového hroznového vína a jablečnou kapsičku Hello 100 %.</div></li></ol><ol class="sc-1tl93fv-10 dnkUhf"><li data-testid="recipe-details-cooking-step" class="sc-1tl93fv-0 brKJtq"><div class="sc-1tl93fv-1 diagqg">1</div><div class="sc-1tl93fv-2 bNfpGN">Z tortil odkrojte okraje tak, abyste místo kruhu získali obdélník. Pomažte je sýrem. První obdélník vyskládejte tenkými kolečky okurky. Zarolujte a dvakrát přepulte.</div></li><li data-testid="recipe-details-cooking-step" class="sc-1tl93fv-0 brKJtq"><div class="sc-1tl93fv-1 diagqg">2</div><div class="sc-1tl93fv-2 bNfpGN">Druhou tortilu vyskládejte šunkou, sýrem a postupujte stejně jako u první rolky.</div></li><li data-testid="recipe-details-cooking-step" class="sc-1tl93fv-0 brKJtq"><div class="sc-1tl93fv-1 diagqg">3</div><div class="sc-1tl93fv-2 bNfpGN">Svačinu doplňte o minibalení bezpeckového hroznového vína a jablečnou kapsičku Hello 100 %.</div></li></ol></div><div data-testid="additional recipe details" class="sc-mqb5tm-6 SDSoQ"><div class="sc-mqb5tm-11 gnzcXh"><div data-testid="recipe-details-rating-heading" class="sc-1svlpub-0 hejWpI"><h2 class="sc-1vohui3-0 jPbFQc" data-testid="styled-title" data-stellar="st-web-title" id="">Hodnocení</h2><div data-testid="recipe-details-rating-result-stars-container" aria-label="4 z 5 hvězdiček" class="sc-lka5vz-1 eOQKaT"><div aria-hidden="true" data-testid="recipe-details-rating-result-star" data-star-result-filled="true" class="sc-lka5vz-0 hxVbse"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="100%" height="100%" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M13.89 3.84a2 2 0 0 0-3.78 0l-.94 2.72a2 2 0 0 1-1.85 1.35l-2.88.06a2 2 0 0 0-1.17 3.59l2.3 1.74a2 2 0 0 1 .7 2.17l-.83 2.76a2 2 0 0 0 3.05 2.22l2.37-1.65a2 2 0 0 1 2.28 0l2.37 1.65a2 2 0 0 0 3.05-2.22l-.83-2.76a2 2 0 0 1 .7-2.17l2.3-1.74a2 2 0 0 0-1.17-3.6l-2.88-.05a2 2 0 0 1-1.85-1.35z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div><div aria-hidden="true" data-testid="recipe-details-rating-result-star" data-star-result-filled="true" class="sc-lka5vz-0 hxVbse"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="100%" height="100%" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M13.89 3.84a2 2 0 0 0-3.78 0l-.94 2.72a2 2 0 0 1-1.85 1.35l-2.88.06a2 2 0 0 0-1.17 3.59l2.3 1.74a2 2 0 0 1 .7 2.17l-.83 2.76a2 2 0 0 0 3.05 2.22l2.37-1.65a2 2 0 0 1 2.28 0l2.37 1.65a2 2 0 0 0 3.05-2.22l-.83-2.76a2 2 0 0 1 .7-2.17l2.3-1.74a2 2 0 0 0-1.17-3.6l-2.88-.05a2 2 0 0 1-1.85-1.35z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div><div aria-hidden="true" data-testid="recipe-details-rating-result-star" data-star-result-filled="true" class="sc-lka5vz-0 hxVbse"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="100%" height="100%" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M13.89 3.84a2 2 0 0 0-3.78 0l-.9