<p>Našli jste v receptu chybu či nesrovnalost? Napište nám ji na <a class="sc-5ttvy-0 gByJsZ" data-testid="text-link" data-stellar="st-web-textLink" href="/prodejny-kontakt">info@albert.cz</a> a my recept vyladíme.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-1lkr4p6-5 jupJOs"><section data-stellar="Recipes-Carousel" aria-label="Podobné recepty Karusel" class="sc-1xtfjm2-0 dSUImK"><div class="sc-1xtfjm2-6 btyeFo"><h2 class="sc-1vohui3-0 czYnWA sc-1xtfjm2-7 HaueD" data-testid="styled-title" data-stellar="st-web-title" id="">Podobné recepty</h2></div><div class="sc-1xtfjm2-3 jUywQu"><div data-stellar="st-web-carousel" data-testid="recipes-carousel-wrapper"><div data-testid="carousel-content-wrapper" class="sc-i1h8z2-0 bLAjLi"><div data-testid="scrollbar" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden; width: 100%; height: auto; min-height: 0px; background: inherit;"><ul class="sc-1xtfjm2-4 eWSHJf" style="position: relative; overflow: scroll; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 0px;"></ul><div aria-hidden="true" data-testid="horizontal-track" class="sc-8tfl60-3 dkYMim" style="position: absolute; display: none;"><div aria-hidden="true" class="sc-1bhy0jv-0 iwchjk"></div></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="sc-8tfl60-4 iuYMEd" style="position: absolute; width: 6px; display: none;"><div aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; width: 100%;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div data-testid="one-half" data-ab-visibility="visible" class="sc-qv30oi-2 ifFwAy"><div data-testid="restriction-wrapper" data-restriction="true" data-isrestrictedmobile="true" data-isrestricteddesktop="false" class="sc-m28gtc-1 hjhJNC"></div></div><div data-testid="one-half" data-ab-visibility="visible" class="sc-qv30oi-2 ifFwAy"><div data-testid="restriction-wrapper" data-restriction="true" data-isrestrictedmobile="true" data-isrestricteddesktop="false" class="sc-m28gtc-1 hjhJNC"></div></div><div data-testid="full-width" data-ab-visibility="